OL,3,CAlmost 300 jobs at risk at chemicals
OL,4,Cfactory in Barry
OL,6,FHundreds of jobs are at risk at a
OL,7,Fchemical giant's Welsh factory.
OL,9,FUS company Dow has confirmed to the
OL,10,Funion Unite that it is closing down an
OL,11,Farea of its plant in Barry, Vale of
OL,12,FGlamorgan.
OL,14,FUnite say that almost 300 jobs are at
OL,15,Frisk due to this closure.
