OL,3,CAlmost 300 jobs at risk at chemicals
OL,4,Cfactory in Barry
OL,6,FThe company, which produces a wide
OL,7,Frange of silicon products, has
OL,8,Foperated from the Barry site since
OL,9,F1971 when it bought the site from
OL,10,FMidland Silicones, and now employs 850
OL,11,Fpeople on a 160-acre site.
OL,13,FA statement from Dow confirmed that
OL,14,Fthe shutdown of basic siloxanes
OL,15,Foperations at Barry has been
OL,16,Fidentified as a "potential outcome".
OL,17,FIt added that this would affect 291
OL,18,Femployees at the Barry site over the
OL,19,Fnext three to four years.
