OL,6,FDow, which has more than 200
OL,7,Fmanufacturing sites across the world,
OL,8,Fwas among the three largest chemical
OL,9,Fproducers in the world in 2021.
OL,10,FHowever, it says cheap competition
OL,11,Ffrom abroad is behind the closure, as
OL,12,Fits basics product are no longer
OL,13,Fcompetitive on the open market.
OL,15,FThe announcement comes after Dow
OL,16,Fconfirmed potential job cuts on
OL,17,FJanuary 31.
