OL,3,CAlmost 300 jobs at risk at chemicals
OL,4,Cfactory in Barry
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid: "It is outrageous that valued
OL,8,Fworkers are being punished for a
OL,9,Fsituation not of their control. The
OL,10,Fpotential loss of so many well-paid
OL,11,Fjobs in the area will be devastating,
OL,12,Fnot just to our members and their
OL,13,Ffamilies, but to the local economy as
OL,14,Fwell."
