OL,3,CAlmost 300 jobs at risk at chemicals
OL,4,Cfactory in Barry
OL,6,FUnite regional officer Richard Jackson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Unite is calling on Dow to
OL,8,Freconsider its decision and work with
OL,9,Fus, government and other stake holders
OL,10,Fto find an alternative solution to
OL,11,Fthis closure. Unite is also calling on
OL,12,FDow to work with the union in order to
OL,13,Favoid compulsory redundancies and to
OL,14,Fseek to protect as many jobs as
OL,15,Fpossible. The union will ensure it is
OL,16,Finvolved all the way throughout this
OL,17,Fprocess."
